    Fine art, illustration & design

    Hi, I'm Tinneke. I create feminine, expressive, and playful paintings & illustrations for your interior or business. In addition, I also offer unique greeting cards and stationery

     

    MY STORY

    Latest news
    ​

    WELCOME TO MY STUDIO!

     

    I'm super excited to share some cool stuff that's happening in my art studio.

    ​

    Renovating our garden studio: a dream is coming true

    We're renovating our garden studio to make it the ultimate creative hub. Picture this: sunshine pouring in, surrounded by trees, and a cozy space filled with art. It's gonna be awesome!

    ​

    New painting collection

    I'm also working on some new paintings. They're all about capturing the beauty and strength of women in our daily lives. Think big, beautiful canvases with flowing brushstrokes and strong, natural colors. Can't wait to show you!

    ​

    Join me on this Journey

    I'd love for you to come along for the ride. Keep an eye on my website and newsletter for updates on the studio makeover and sneak peeks of the paintings.

     

    Catch you later,

    Tinneke

     

    Subscribe to my email list to be the first to know about my latest news, events, exclusive offers, and more!
